HEADWORD: Improbate
<hw>Im"pro*bate</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>improbatus</ets>, p. p. of <ets>improbare</ets> to disapprove;
pref. <ets>im-</ets> not + <ets>probare</ets> to approve.]</ety> <def>To
disapprove of; to disallow.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
